title: 103. Limiting Beliefs and How They Affect Our Desires
description:
Happy Thursday! 

This week is allll about limiting beliefs. Ever feel like you desire something but for some reason it "can't" happen for you? Like maybe you desire to be in a committed relationship but end up attracting partners who want nothing to do with commitment? Tune in to find out how limiting beliefs can be holding you back from your desires.

Psssst if you would like to enroll in the self-study version of Self Love Over Codependency, you can still enroll here, we would love to have you!
